title: D2
description:
In ancient China, the Cathay faction is tragically split.  Followers of the Temple have picked up their swords and is at war with the Imperials.  We are about to witness the bloodiest battle of the war.  They are fighting for a large fishing village!  Enjoy :D

This a Mod for Attila Total War, you can find it in the steam workshop!  Enjoy.
